A '''vitapill''' was a small herbal stimulant in pill form, a combination of [[Drall/Legends|Drallish]] herbs and [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] emulsion. It worked as a short-term health booster. Multiple pills taken within a 21-hour period, or Drallish day, were cumulatively less effective. Vitapills were available for sale to offworlders in [[Meccha]].<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

